[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0474","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0758","title":"Netscape Enterprise 与 FastTrack Web 服务器源代码泄露漏洞","description":"该漏洞存在于 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 与 Netscape FastTrack Server 3.01 中。服务器在处理 URL 时未能正确处理 URL 编码的空格字符（%20），当攻击者向一个 CGI 脚本或服务器端脚本的 URL 末尾追加 %20 时，服务器会错误地将请求解析为对源文件的访问，从而将本不应返回的脚本源代码直接返回给客户端。攻击无需身份认证，仅需构造包含 %20 的简单 HTTP 请求即可读取服务器端脚本源码，导致应用程序逻辑、内部实现及潜在敏感信息泄露，为后续进一步攻击提供线索。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0758"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级至 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 或 FastTrack Server 3.02 及以上版本；临时缓解可在 Web 服务器前部署反向代理或重写规则，拒绝 URL 路径中包含 %20 编码的脚本请求，并限制对脚本源文件的直接访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0758","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0758.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0474.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1145","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1145.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1515","title":"TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0 存在配置缺陷漏洞，该产品在处理消息时因发送方和收件人地址验证逻辑异常而导致无限循环状态。当攻击者发送包含不正确地址信息的消息时，系统会持续以 10 秒为周期尝试返回消息，导致 CPU 资源消耗激增，服务器响应变慢直至服务完全不可用。该漏洞影响范围广泛，任何未正确配置 TFS Gateway 的用户都可能成为目标，攻击者无需任何权限即可远程触发。漏洞原理在于网关未能正确识别和过滤错误地址消息的处理流程，致使程序进入无限重试状态，暴露了系统在异常输入处理方面的严重不足，为攻击者提供了利用 WSGI 协议实现服务拒绝的便利手段，影响企业的网络通讯服务稳定性和用户体验。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1515"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.357","remediation":"升级 TenFour TFS Gateway 至修复了该问题的后续版本（4.0 之后的官方补丁版本）；若无法立即升级，可在网关配置中禁用或修正导致异常的「非默认发送方/接收方地址」处理规则，并将可疑来源 IP 在防火墙处阻断，以减少恶意消息触发网关每 10 秒持续重发所导致的拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/613","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3290","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19477","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f56f639de76f94fc0aef783754a3de16fea7357b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1515","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1515.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/be19cdaa6196942fd4096a42a1eaf047a8584298/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68q7-2qpc-87mh/GHSA-68q7-2qpc-87mh.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/613/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d8232fe3e2556046ab374e149ecb1f50a314b074/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1145.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0503","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0774","title":"Martin Stover Mars NetWare Emulation 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Martin Stover 开发的 Mars NetWare Emulation（NWE，即 mars_nwe）软件包存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，其根源在于程序在处理目录名称时未对输入长度进行边界校验，将过长的目录名直接拷贝至固定大小的栈缓冲区中，从而触发缓冲区溢出。该漏洞影响 mars_nwe 0.99 及相近版本，主要危害运行该 NetWare 仿真服务的 Linux/Unix 系统。攻击者需具备在受影响系统上创建或访问含超长名称目录的权限（通常为本地用户），通过构造异常长的目录名称即可利用该漏洞改写栈内存并返回地址，实现任意代码执行或导致服务崩溃。利用方式多为本地提权，即普通用户借助溢出发起恶意载荷以获取更高权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0774"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.833","remediation":"建议立即升级 Martin Stower Mars NWE 至修复版本 0.99p（或后续官方版本），从 https://www.comlab.ghg.net/mars_nwe/ 获取并重新编译安装。如无法立即升级，可限制对 NWE 服务的本地目录访问权限、移除不可信用户的本地登录权限，并仅以必要权限运行 mars_nwe 守护进程作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/617","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19485","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7cda0b7fa75f17f1e2b56ef076a6f9175f854ab4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0774.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0774","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0774.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4cacb08131e7c4736ad136de17873dbcaeddf850/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0774.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf4p-xcfq-g2qq/GHSA-wf4p-xcfq-g2qq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0774.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1143","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1513","title":"3Com SuperStack II hub MIB信息泄露漏洞","description":"3Com SuperStack II 集线器运行软件版本 2.10 中的管理信息库（MIB）存在信息泄露漏洞。该 MIB 包含一个对象标识符（.1.3.6.1.4.1.43.10.4.2），通过只读 community 字符串即可访问，但该对象会泄露完整的 community 字符串表，包括读写权限的 community 字符串。攻击者可在未授权情况下通过 SNMP 协议读取该 OID，获取高权限 community 字符串后进一步执行设备配置篡改、信息窃取等未授权操作，严重威胁网络设备安全。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1513"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.093","remediation":"升级 3Com SuperStack II hub 固件至 2.10 以上版本，并在设备 ACL 中限制 SNMP 仅允许受信管理 IP 段访问，同时将 SNMP 读团体字串由默认的 public 改为复杂随机字符串，禁用不必要的 SNMP 服务或使用 SNMPv3 加密认证。如设备已停产，应替换为支持安全 SNMP 的现代设备。最终，建议加固方式是在网络边界防火墙封禁 UDP 161/162 端口的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93616983223090&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1513","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1513.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/44d84714e9a3b4364d62f8189e2d74dba61b570e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gwm8-rgj9-362f/GHSA-gwm8-rgj9-362f.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87920/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1071","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1071.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1354","title":"Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 敏感信息明文存储漏洞","description":"Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 5.506 及更早版本中的 E-mail 客户端存在明文存储敏感信息的漏洞。服务器将用户账号和密码以明文形式保存在本地文件中，包括 5.506 版的 home.fc、3.5 版的 network.fc 以及启用日志时的 FCCLIENT.LOG 文件。本地攻击者若能访问这些文件，即可直接获取用户的凭证信息，进而冒充目标用户登录系统。该漏洞源于程序未对存储的敏感数据进行加密处理。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1354"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.720","remediation":"升级 Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 至 5.506 以上版本。禁用调试日志功能以防止 FCCLIENT.LOG 记录明文凭据。通过文件系统 ACL 严格限制 home.fc、network.fc 和 FCCLIENT.LOG 的访问权限，仅允许必要系统账户读取。若厂商已停止支持，建议迁移至继续维护的邮件服务软件（如 Microsoft Exchange 或 Dovecot）以避免凭据泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93637687305327&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93698283309513&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1354","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1354.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vm2r-v9g5-m7v4/GHSA-vm2r-v9g5-m7v4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000754.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--80742b1f-750a-4cc5-b3e9-d6215f20b69b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1071.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0911","title":"ProFTPD MKD/CWD 命令远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 至 pre5 版本、wu-ftpd 及 beroftpd 等 FTP 服务器软件存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 MKD（创建目录）和 CWD（切换目录）命令序列，构造嵌套目录结构触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞危害严重，攻击者可在完全控制受影响服务器后执行任意代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0911"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.797","remediation":"升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.0rc1 或更高版本，升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.1 或更高版本，升级 beroftpd 至已修复版本。如无法升级，在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用匿名 FTP 写入权限，并限制 MKD/CWD 命令的目录深度。同时建议迁移至仍在维护的 FTP 服务器软件（如 vsftpd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19990210","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/612","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19476","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/83494e95424aced4cfc65648b3019774f7fc51c3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0911.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0911","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0911/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0911.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0911.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7mmm-q9r4-mm4v/GHSA-7mmm-q9r4-mm4v.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9230692740a5b211bda51742c17a001e1943a803/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0911.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/proftpd_pre6_exploit.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/612/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0866","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1016","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9189,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10871}}","description":"Microsoft 的 HTML 控件在 Internet Explorer 5.0、FrontPage Express、Outlook Express 5 及 Eudora 等多款软件中存在拒绝服务漏洞。该漏洞源于 HTML 控件对表单字段的处理逻辑缺陷，当远程攻击者构造包含超大尺寸 HTML 表单字段（如表单元格中的大型文本输入框）的恶意网页或 HTML 邮件时，目标软件在渲染该页面时会陷入持续处理状态，导致 CPU 占用率飙升至 100%。攻击条件为诱使用户访问恶意网站或打开特制 HTML 邮件，无需身份认证或特殊权限，成功利用可使受害者系统失去响应，造成可用性耗尽型拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1016"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.717","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 1 或更高版本（安装微软 1999 年 9 月累积安全更新），FrontPage Express、Outlook Express 5 同步更新至对应补丁版本。临时缓解措施：在 Outlook Express 与 Eudora 中禁用 HTML 邮件预览、以纯文本方式阅读邮件，并使用浏览器安全区域限制自动加载远程网页内容，避免访问不可信站点。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93578772920970&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/606","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19471","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1016.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1016","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/938d5f69569a096cf728175efd0ca15f6fd92c6a/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1016.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_nt_ms02-005.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1016.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1235","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 FTP 密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 在用户通过 FTP 协议访问服务器时，会将登录使用的用户名和密码明文记录在 URL 历史记录中，存储于 index.dat 文件。本地攻击者可通过读取其他用户的 index.dat 文件获取 FTP 凭据，或通过肩窥（shoulder surfing）方式在用户鼠标悬停链接时从状态栏窃取密码。该漏洞影响 IE 5 及早期版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，需本地访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1235"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.410","remediation":"避免使用 Internet Explorer 5 内置 FTP 客户端访问需要认证的 FTP 站点；改用专用 FTP 客户端软件（如 FileZilla）或使用资源管理器的 FTP 功能代替。同时定期清除 IE 历史记录（工具→Internet 选项→清除历史记录），并启用 IE 的「退出时删除浏览历史」策略。建议升级至更高版本 IE 或更换现代浏览器以彻底消除此安全隐患。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ntbugtraq.ntadvice.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9904&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R179","http://packetderm.cotse.com/mailing-lists/ntbugtraq/1999/0364.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3289","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19473","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1235","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87772/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000751.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fe06dc37-1641-4571-a309-13ef3dac15ec.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0669","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0872","title":"Caldera OpenLinux Vixie cron 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie cron 组件在处理 crontab 文件中的 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞，通过向 crontab 文件中写入超长的 MAILTO 变量值触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenLinux 等系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至最新版本或限制 crontab 文件的写入权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0872"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.990","remediation":"升级到 OpenLinux 更新版本的 vixie-cron 包（修复版本见厂商 1999 年安全公告并打全系统补丁）。临时缓解措施：将 crontab 文件及 cron 服务目录权限收紧为仅 root 可写（chmod 600 /etc/crontab 且 chmod 700 /var/spool/cron），并限制普通用户使用 crontab 命令（移除 /usr/bin/crontab 的 setuid 位或仅授权信任用户），避免通过过长 MAILTO 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/759","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4d7236390d3d65194e590e3c8620543620af3984/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0872.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0872","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0872.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0872.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rpr-p9f6-2hhx/GHSA-9rpr-p9f6-2hhx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/759/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--20b2865f-6121-40d9-88ae-cc16ce538ecd.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000750.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0489","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0769","title":"Linux Vixie Cron 计划任务 MAILTO 环境变量注入漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 是 Linux 系统中广泛使用的定时任务守护进程。该漏洞源于 Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时未对输入参数进行充分验证，本地用户可通过构造特制的 MAILTO 环境变量值，向系统 sendmail 命令注入恶意参数，进而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenLinux 2.2、Debian 2.1/2.2 以及 RedHat 6.0 等早期 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2。攻击者需具备本地登录权限，通过在 crontab 配置或环境变量中设置恶意 MAILTO 值即可触发，导致权限提升或系统被进一步控制。建议用户升级至修正后的 Vixie Cron 版本，或通过限制本地用户环境变量写入权限来缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0769"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.193","remediation":"建议升级 Vixie Cron 至各发行版已修复版本：Debian 用户升级至 cron 3.0pl1-57 及以上，RedHat 用户安装 vixie-cron 更新包，Caldera 用户应用对应的安全补丁。升级后 MAILTO 环境变量将不再被用于拼接 sendmail 命令参数。如无法立即升级，可临时限制普通用户对 crontab 的使用权限（通过 /etc/cron.allow 和 /etc/cron.deny 控制），并加强对 crontab 提交内容的审计。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19474","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0769","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0769.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9qf9-2h54-chr8/GHSA-9qf9-2h54-chr8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990830.data","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--96d6bfc3-3242-4258-a570-581568f1a763.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0489.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0489.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0483","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0768","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9208,\"outputTokens\":29,\"totalTokens\":10901}}","description":"Vixie Cron 在 Red Hat Linux 及 S.u.S.E. Linux 系统上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过特制的 MAILTO 环境变量值触发该漏洞。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 以及 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.0/6.1 等版本。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可在 cron 任务中设置超长的 MAILTO 环境变量值，当系统尝试向该地址发送邮件通知时，cron 进程将触发缓冲区溢出，攻击者可能借此获得 root 权限执行任意代码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0768"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.067","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及以上版本或 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 及以上版本，并安装厂商发布的 Vixie Cron 安全补丁（如 Red Hat RPM 更新包）。如无法立即升级，可临时删除或限制 crontab 中 MAILTO 环境变量的使用，并将 /usr/bin/crontab 权限收紧为仅 root 可写，以降低被本地用户利用缓冲区溢出提权的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/602","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19470","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0768","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0768.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q395-vm9c-r75g/GHSA-q395-vm9c-r75g.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0905","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1052","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10796,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"Microsoft FrontPage 在默认配置下会将网站表单提交的结果保存于文档根目录下的 /_private/form_results.txt 文件中，该文件具有全局可读权限且可直接通过 HTTP 访问。由于该路径为默认位置且未进行访问控制，远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标站点发起普通的 HTTP GET 请求即可读取此文件内容，从而获取其他用户通过表单提交的敏感信息，如姓名、邮箱、电话、留言等个人数据。该漏洞影响使用默认配置且未修改该文件权限或移除该文件的 Microsoft FrontPage 网站，属于信息泄露类配置缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1052"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.350","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft FrontPage 2000 或更高版本，并在 Web 服务器中删除站点根目录下 /_private/form_results.txt 文件。将表单结果保存路径移出 Web 文档根目录，或在 Web 服务器配置中拒绝对该目录的匿名访问（如用 .htaccess 或 IIS 目录权限设置为不可列出、不可读取），对表单提交内容做访问控制与加密存储以缓解信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582550911564&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1052","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d7bfe9c86213fdf5ad56116fa46ee20a047ec9da/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88081/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0320","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0320.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0720","title":"glibc pt_chown 权限提升漏洞","description":"glibc 2.1.1 及之前版本中的 pt_chown 辅助程序被安装为 setuid root，本地普通用户可利用该程序在伪终端（PTY）设备上修改属主与权限，从而获取其他用户的控制终端访问权限，实现本地权限提升。攻击者需具备本地登录权限，通过精心构造的请求使 pt_chown 错误地将 TTY 设备归属到攻击者的 UID，进而读取或注入其他用户的终端会话内容。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0720"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"将系统 glibc 升级至 2.1.2 或更高版本，该版本已移除 pt_chown 的 setuid 权限，消除本地用户借由 pt_chown 篡改其他用户 TTY 设备进而提权的风险。如短期内无法升级，应立即执行 chmod u-s /usr/lib/pt_chown 去掉 setuid 位，或在确认无依赖后删除该二进制文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/597","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=lcamtuf.4.05.9907041223290.355-300000%40nimue.ids.pl","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19467","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0720.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0320.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0320.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0320.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1689","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1064","title":"WindowMaker 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WindowMaker 桌面环境 0.52 至 0.60.0 版本中存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过执行 WindowMaker 时传入超长的程序名称（argv[0]）参数，可触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响面较广，利用方式简单，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1064"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.880","remediation":"升级 Window Maker 至 0.61.0 及以上版本（当前最新稳定版为 0.96.0），该版本修复了 wdefaults.c 中 strcpy 未做边界检查导致的缓冲区溢出问题。可通过系统包管理器（apt install wmaker / dnf install wmaker）直接更新。如无法升级，可在启动脚本中限制 argv[0] 长度不超过 249 字符作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93555317429630&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582070508957&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/596"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0878","title":"WU-FTPD MAPPING_CHDIR 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 及相关 FTP 服务器在处理 MAPPING_CHDIR 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的超长 MAPPING_CHDIR 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 WU-FTPD 及其衍生 FTP 服务器软件，攻击者只需能够连接到目标 FTP 服务的 21 端口即可利用，利用难度低，可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0878"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-08-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"WU-FTPD 已停止维护多年，官方未发布安全补丁。建议立即停止使用 WU-FTPD，迁移至受支持且无此漏洞的替代 FTP 服务器软件，如 vsftpd 3.0.x、ProFTPD 1.3.x 或 Pure-FTPD 最新稳定版。如无法立即迁移，应在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 服务的访问来源 IP，仅允许可信网络段访问，并禁用不必要的 FTP 功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/599","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0878"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml"}]